on that reputation,

199
00:07:44,781 --> 00:07:47,315
to make Seattle Grace a
place where medical innovation

200
00:07:47,384 --> 00:07:49,817
is developed and delivered

201
00:07:49,886 --> 00:07:52,019
to the patients who need it.

202
00:07:53,523 --> 00:07:55,022
That is our plan.

203
00:07:55,092 --> 00:07:57,158
That is the future
of Seattle Grace.

204
00:07:57,227 --> 00:07:59,527
And we invite you
to be a part of it.

205
00:08:09,289 --> 00:08:10,455
Neat.

206
00:08:14,111 --> 00:08:17,094
