228
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:22,177
Oh! Yes.

229
00:09:25,164 --> 00:09:26,230
Brooks.

230
00:09:27,133 --> 00:09:28,415
Brooks, what's the story?

231
00:09:28,484 --> 00:09:30,696
I'm sorry, but I'm on
Bailey's service today,

232
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,198
